---
const supportItems = [
  { text: 'Respuesta Rápida', icon: 'bi-lightning-fill' },
  { text: 'Soporte 24/7', icon: 'bi-headset' },
  { text: 'Personal Calificado', icon: 'bi-person-heart' },
  { text: 'Mantenimiento Proactivo', icon: 'bi-wrench-adjustable' }
];
---

<section id="support" class="bg-white py-20 section-animate">
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
    <div class="flex-1 order-2 md:order-1 animate-slide-left">
      <img 
        src="/images/about/Tutelkan_Asistencia_Tecnica_Web.webp" 
        alt="Soporte técnico Tutelkan" 
        class="w-full" 
      />
    </div>
    <div class="flex-1 order-1 md:order-2 animate-slide-right">
      <div class="mb-4">
        <span class="text-[#cf3339] font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">SOPORTE Y MANTENCIÓN</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 leading-tight">
        Asistencia técnica ininterrumpida: 
        <span class="text-[#cf3339]">Tu confianza, nuestra prioridad</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        Nuestro compromiso es garantizar que tus operaciones nunca se detengan, 
        ofreciendo un soporte técnico y servicios de mantenimiento que están a la 
        altura de tus expectativas.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        {supportItems.map((item, index) => (
          <button 
            class={`relative overflow-hidden bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 px-6 py-5 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:text-white animate-fade-scale animate-delay-${index + 3} group`} 
            aria-label={item.text}
          >
            <span class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#cf3339] transform -translate-x-full group-hover:translate-x-0 transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out"></span>
            <span class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-start gap-4 text-left">
              <i class={`bi ${item.icon} text-[#cf3339] group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 text-xl flex-shrink-0`}></i>
              <span class="text-left">{item.text}</span>
            </span>
          </button>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>



<script type="module" src="/src/scripts/sections/support.js"></script>